  %% Diagram 79: Vendor Acquisition Funnel and Conversion Flywheel

  Awareness[Awareness\nfield sales + Facebook groups + referrals + academy content]
  Lead[Qualified lead]
  Demo[Product demo]
  Onboard[Onboarded vendor]
  Active[Active revenue-generating vendor]
  Refer[Referral to new vendors]

  Drop{Funnel drop-off?}
  Recover[Targeted intervention\nfollow-up, incentives, training]

  Awareness --> Lead --> Demo --> Onboard --> Active --> Refer --> Awareness

  Lead --> Drop
  Demo --> Drop
  Onboard --> Drop
  Drop -- Yes --> Recover --> Lead
  Drop -- No --> Active
